        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>电流源电路学习笔记</h1><h2 id="电流源在电路中的作用">电流源在电路中的作用</h2><ul><li>电流源电路为各级电路提供合适的静态电流；</li><li>作为有源负载代替高阻值的电阻，提高放大电路的放大能力。</li></ul><h2 id="基本电流源电路">基本电流源电路</h2><h3 id="镜像电流源">镜像电流源</h3><p>电路示意如图所示<br><img src="/2021/05/29/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%8D%95%E5%85%83%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%81%92%E6%B5%81%E6%BA%90%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF/%E9%95%9C%E5%83%8F%E7%94%B5%E6%B5%81%E6%BA%90%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF.png" alt="镜像电流源电路"></p><ol><li>由于 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>Q</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">Q_1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal">Q</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.30110799999999993em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">1</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 管 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><semantics><mrow><msub><mi>V</mi><mi>C</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msub><mi>V</mi><mi>B</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">V_C=V_B</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.83333em;vertical-align:-0.15em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathnormal" style="margin-right:0.22222em;">V</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="v